Future grants can only be applied to schema objects.

From the documentation&quot;When a database is cloned, the schemas in the cloned database copy the future privileges from the source schemas. This maintains consistency with the regular object grants, in which the grants of the source object (i.e. database) are not copied to the clone, but the grants on all the children objects (i.e. schemas in the database) are copied to the clones.&quot;

Future grants cannot be applied to databases. 

1. USE ROLE ACCOUNTADMIN;
